h: Rajasthan: 9 killed in jeep-bus collision in Bhilwara
sub_h: As many as nine people died while 10 others sustained injuries when the jeep they were travelling in collided with a RSRTC bus late on Monday in Bhilwara district. The accident happened near Bigod on Kota-Bhilwara highway.

h: Jaipur: Wedding postponed after two sisters die in accident
sub_h: The deceased sisters identified as 19-year-old Kajal Mishra and her elder sister, 24-year-old Nivedita Mishra who were travelling with five other relatives in the same bus.

h: Rajasthan: 11 killed in bus-truck collision on NH-11 in Bikaner, several critically injured
sub_h: At least 10 people were killed and over dozens injured when a truck collided with a bus full of passengers on National Highway-11 near Sri Dungargarh in Rajasthan's Bikaner district at around 7.45am on Monday.
